{
  "id": "6a27ec0fa39111a243de9383",
  "title": "輪郭は単なるメモ",
  "created": 1781001232,
  "updated": 1781001325,
  "lines": [
    {
      "id": "6a27ec0fa39111a243de9383",
      "text": "輪郭は単なるメモ",
      "userId": "58d101391094b20011d8c2f4",
      "created": 1781001232,
      "updated": 1781001232
    },
    {
      "id": "6a27ec100000000000240a6f",
      "text": "[デライト.icon]",
      "userId": "58d101391094b20011d8c2f4",
      "created": 1781001232,
      "updated": 1781001253
    },
    {
      "id": "6a27ec100000000000240a71",
      "text": "[輪郭]そのものは変哲のないメモと捉えて使っている[zatsma.icon]",
      "userId": "58d101391094b20011d8c2f4",
      "created": 1781001232,
      "updated": 1781001238
    },
    {
      "id": "6a27ec100000000000240a72",
      "text": " 要素だけ見ると普通じゃない？",
      "userId": "58d101391094b20011d8c2f4",
      "created": 1781001232,
      "updated": 1781001232
    },
    {
      "id": "6a27ec100000000000240a73",
      "text": "  タイトル",
      "userId": "58d101391094b20011d8c2f4",
      "created": 1781001232,
      "updated": 1781001232
    },
    {
      "id": "6a27ec100000000000240a74",
      "text": "  本文",
      "userId": "58d101391094b20011d8c2f4",
      "created": 1781001232,
      "updated": 1781001232
    },
    {
      "id": "6a27ec100000000000240a75",
      "text": "  ID",
      "userId": "58d101391094b20011d8c2f4",
      "created": 1781001232,
      "updated": 1781001232
    },
    {
      "id": "6a27ec100000000000240a76",
      "text": " [引き入れ]によってメモ同士の関係を作る点がデライトの独特さと考えられる",
      "userId": "58d101391094b20011d8c2f4",
      "created": 1781001232,
      "updated": 1781001232
    },
    {
      "id": "6a27ec100000000000240a77",
      "text": "  とはいえリンクが作れるメモツール自体は珍しくない(セルフツッコミ)",
      "userId": "58d101391094b20011d8c2f4",
      "created": 1781001232,
      "updated": 1781001232
    },
    {
      "id": "6a27ec100000000000240a78",
      "text": " 実は[引き入れ]とかしなくても使える",
      "userId": "58d101391094b20011d8c2f4",
      "created": 1781001232,
      "updated": 1781001325
    },
    {
      "id": "6a27ec100000000000240a79",
      "text": "  実際引き入れをほとんどしないデライターも居る",
      "userId": "58d101391094b20011d8c2f4",
      "created": 1781001232,
      "updated": 1781001232
    },
    {
      "id": "6a27ec100000000000240a7a",
      "text": "   n=1",
      "userId": "58d101391094b20011d8c2f4",
      "created": 1781001232,
      "updated": 1781001232
    },
    {
      "id": "6a27ec100000000000240a7b",
      "text": "  気軽な公開メモとしての運用と思われる[zatsma.icon]",
      "userId": "58d101391094b20011d8c2f4",
      "created": 1781001232,
      "updated": 1781001232
    },
    {
      "id": "6a27ec100000000000240a7c",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "58d101391094b20011d8c2f4",
      "created": 1781001232,
      "updated": 1781001232
    }
  ]
}